          "speakerTag": 4,
          "text": "You insolent brat! I'm a general! Show your respect!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0020.zt1",
          "speaker": "Agger",
          "speakerTag": 4,
          "text": "Disobey my command, will you?  Then our contract is VOID!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "03000100",
      "count": 44,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0233.zt1",
          "speaker": "Neive",
          "speakerTag": 3,
          "text": "Me?  What are YOU doing here? I thought you were in K'sil."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0260.zt1",
          "speaker": "Neive",
          "speakerTag": 3,
          "text": "And some enemies as well. ha ha ha."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0350.zt1",
          "speaker": "Neive",
          "speakerTag": 3,
          "text": "The wind is too strong... our !c00ff00Battleship!cffffff can't move forward."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0353.zt1",
          "speaker": "Neive",
          "speakerTag": 3,
          "text": "Hmm... It's difficult dealing with all three races at the same time."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0400.zt1",
          "speaker": "Neive",
          "speakerTag": 3,
          "text": "I'll help!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "01040300",
      "count": 42,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0020.zt1",
          "speaker": "Vincent",
          "speakerTag": 0,
          "text": "What? How did you even manage to..."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0021.zt1",
          "speaker": "Vincent",
          "speakerTag": 0,
          "text": "Panzers?"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0030.zt1",
          "speaker": "Vincent",
          "speakerTag": 0,
          "text": "Supplies? I thought the general took care of those."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0123.zt1",
          "speaker": "Vincent",
          "speakerTag": 0,
          "text": "Err? Why?"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0130.zt1",
          "speaker": "Vincent",
          "speakerTag": 0,
          "text": "Huh? What's that?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "01090100",
      "count": 38,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0043.zt1",
          "speaker": "Theon",
          "speakerTag": 12,
          "text": "My apologies. Are you the Marching Mercenaries?"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0210.zt1",
          "speaker": "Theon",
          "speakerTag": 12,
          "text": "Ha ha ha, like I said before, I'm here for the future of Drusilla."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0213.zt1",
          "speaker": "Theon",
          "speakerTag": 12,
          "text": "Ha ha ha... Okay, let's finish excavating for the Phoenix."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0450.zt1",
          "speaker": "Theon",
          "speakerTag": 12,
          "text": "Easily. Ha ha ha."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0623.zt1",
          "speaker": "Theon",
          "speakerTag": 12,
          "text": "Ha ha, did you forget my name already? Call me !c00ffffTheon!cffffff."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "01010000",
      "count": 38,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0122.zt1",
          "speaker": "Lantere",
          "speakerTag": 13,
          "text": "..."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0533.zt1",
          "speaker": "Lantere",
          "speakerTag": 13,
          "text": "We're just following Council orders, it was to invade the Hume."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0800.zt1",
          "speaker": "Lantere",
          "speakerTag": 13,
          "text": "I know it is, and it's why I'm here.  As a matter of fact, I'm your !c00ffffAdjutant!cffffff as of today."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0800.zt1",
          "speaker": "Lantere",
          "speakerTag": 13,
          "text": "Looks like you're having preparation issues.  Let me take care of that."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0804.zt1",
          "speaker": "Lantere",
          "speakerTag": 13,
          "text": "The purple bar on the upper right side is the enemy tower's HP."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "030a05010a0200",
      "count": 38,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0240.zt1",
          "speaker": "Helba",
          "speakerTag": 6,
          "text": "Where are my brothers? "
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0400.zt1",
          "speaker": "Helba",
          "speakerTag": 6,
          "text": "The Elven?! Those weasels!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0460.zt1",
          "speaker": "Helba",
          "speakerTag": 6,
          "text": "Who are you!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0460.zt1",
          "speaker": "Helba",
          "speakerTag": 6,
          "text": "So you're the one!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0461.zt1",
          "speaker": "Helba",
          "speakerTag": 6,
          "text": "Just what have you done..."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "040403050500",
      "count": 37,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0043.zt1",
          "speaker": "Cecil",
          "speakerTag": 1,
          "text": "We don't want to kill you. Tell us what you were saying earlier."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0043.zt1",
          "speaker": "Cecil",
          "speakerTag": 1,
          "text": "I remember Gramps saying something similar."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0043.zt1",
          "speaker": "Cecil",
          "speakerTag": 1,
          "text": "Vincent, we should listen to him."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0093.zt1",
          "speaker": "Cecil",
          "speakerTag": 1,
          "text": "That can't be coincidence... can it?"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0093.zt1",
          "speaker": "Cecil",
          "speakerTag": 1,
          "text": "Now now, we have no time to be wasting like this."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "03070501070200",
      "count": 37,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0923.zt1",
          "speaker": "Juno",
          "speakerTag": 11,
          "text": "Where are your manners, stranger!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0993.zt1",
          "speaker": "Juno",
          "speakerTag": 11,
          "text": "Answer him, or I'll end you!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0993.zt1",
          "speaker": "Juno",
          "speakerTag": 11,
          "text": "Let's find their lab..."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/1040.zt1",
          "speaker": "Juno",
          "speakerTag": 11,
          "text": "You're playing God. I won't forgive you for this!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/1041.zt1",
          "speaker": "Juno",
          "speakerTag": 11,
          "text": "I'll end you right here...  and I'll save Lantere myself."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "prefixHex": "03060100",
      "count": 36,
      "samples": [
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0400.zt1",
          "speaker": "Arang",
          "speakerTag": 7,
          "text": "Warrior !c00ffffHelba!cffffff."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0483.zt1",
          "speaker": "Arang",
          "speakerTag": 7,
          "text": "Yes, their number is many... far too many."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0490.zt1",
          "speaker": "Arang",
          "speakerTag": 7,
          "text": "Not good. !cff37ffBeril!cffffff was wiped out."
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0501.zt1",
          "speaker": "Arang",
          "speakerTag": 7,
          "text": "Careful, he's the commander of the Hume expeditionary force!"
        },
        {
          "path": "assets/script_eng/0503.zt1",
          "speaker": "Arang",
          "speakerTag": 7,
          "text": "Helba, let's go!"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
